Oat: The Flash.

01:07:20.200 --> 01:07:22.340
Off: That feels good.

01:07:22.340 --> 01:07:24.440
[Satisfied. OK.]

01:07:24.440 --> 01:07:25.640
Off: Fast and fierce.

01:07:26.200 --> 01:07:26.900
Off: Fast and fierce.

01:07:26.900 --> 01:07:27.700
Oat: Brother!

01:07:28.120 --> 01:07:29.200
Phuak: Blue Demon.

01:07:30.230 --> 01:07:32.340
[Pop replaces Oat and joins the team]

01:07:32.760 --> 01:07:33.520
NuNew: Hello.

01:07:33.520 --> 01:07:34.200
Ink: Hello.

01:07:34.200 --> 01:07:34.840
Pop: Hello.

01:07:34.840 --> 01:07:35.060
Hello everyone.

01:07:35.060 --> 01:07:35.800
[Welcome to Running Man]

01:07:35.800 --> 01:07:35.940
Ink: Sorry, but the person
you picked is like…

01:07:35.940 --> 01:07:37.600
[How are we supposed to push him at all?]

01:07:37.600 --> 01:07:38.560
NuNew: Who can beat him?

01:07:38.560 --> 01:07:38.860
Ink: Same type of player.
We can't push him at all.

01:07:38.860 --> 01:07:40.820
[How is anyone supposed to win like this?]

01:07:40.840 --> 01:07:40.980
Daou: I'm desperate.

01:07:40.980 --> 01:07:41.860
[I feel like giving up]

01:07:42.080 --> 01:07:42.380
Daou: The original one's a moving tank.

01:07:42.380 --> 01:07:43.700
[At first it was just
a moving tank]

01:07:44.040 --> 01:07:44.140
Daou: This is a cannon.

01:07:44.140 --> 01:07:45.540
[Now it's a cannon]

01:07:45.540 --> 01:07:46.800
Daou: This is a cannon.

01:07:47.470 --> 01:07:47.820
Pop: Keep bragging all you want, kids.

01:07:47.820 --> 01:07:49.300
[Let's settle this
with everything we've got]

01:07:49.500 --> 01:07:50.800
[Hypes up the atmosphere]

01:07:50.800 --> 01:07:51.620
Pop: I'll show you
real strength later.

01:07:51.620 --> 01:07:53.300
[I'll show you the real strength soon]

01:07:54.480 --> 01:07:56.940
Ten: The tension just
shot through the roof.

01:07:57.780 --> 01:07:59.840
[Can we expect something from Pop?]

01:07:59.840 --> 01:08:01.540
PD: Today's name-tag ripping game
rules are as follows.

01:08:01.540 --> 01:08:02.280
[Final Round:
Name Tag Ripping Battle Rules]

01:08:02.280 --> 01:08:04.480
PD: We'll compete in teams

01:08:04.480 --> 01:08:04.820
PD: The key point is
the HP
everyone accumulated since this morning.

01:08:04.820 --> 01:08:06.220
[Name tag ripping: deduct HP]

01:08:06.220 --> 01:08:09.480
[Name tag ripping: deduct HP]

01:08:09.480 --> 01:08:09.620
PD: For teams with 3 lives—

01:08:09.620 --> 01:08:11.680
[For example, if there are 3 lives,]

01:08:11.680 --> 01:08:13.580
PD: Three players,
meaning 1 life per person。

01:08:13.580 --> 01:08:14.160
[Blue Team: Off; Phuak; Pop]
[If 3 members are out, the mission fails]

01:08:14.160 --> 01:08:17.520
PD: If all 3 name tags are ripped,
the team is eliminated.

01:08:17.520 --> 01:08:18.319
Off: OK.

01:08:18.319 --> 01:08:20.200
PD: As for the team with only 2 lives—

01:08:20.200 --> 01:08:20.760
PD: That means
the entire team shares 2 lives

01:08:20.760 --> 01:08:24.600
[Pink Team: Jeff; Ten; Ink]
[If 2 members are out, the mission fails]

01:08:24.600 --> 01:08:27.359
PD: If 2 out of the 3 have
their name tags ripped,

01:08:27.840 --> 01:08:28.569
PD: the whole team will be eliminated.

01:08:28.569 --> 01:08:30.529
PD: And this team here has 4 lives.

01:08:30.840 --> 01:08:32.479
PD: You have 3 players, right?
[Yellow Team: NuNew; Blue; Daou]
[Even if 3 members are out, 1 life remains]

01:08:32.479 --> 01:08:33.800
PD: Each person has 1 life.

01:08:33.800 --> 01:08:35.399
PD: And there is 1 extra life.

01:08:36.470 --> 01:08:37.229
NuNew: I see.

01:08:37.819 --> 01:08:38.040
[Special items will
appear during the game]

01:08:38.040 --> 01:08:39.240
PD: During the game.

01:08:41.240 --> 01:08:41.920
Phuak: Again.

01:08:41.920 --> 01:08:43.680
PD: The map is divided into 3 zones.

01:08:43.680 --> 01:08:43.700
PD: As long as you find 3 puzzle pieces
and assemble them,

01:08:43.700 --> 01:08:47.180
[Life Card puzzle pieces
are hidden throughout the area]

01:08:47.520 --> 01:08:49.100
PD: you can gain 1 extra life.

01:08:49.100 --> 01:08:51.640
[Collect 3 fragments to gain 1 life;
Running Man Thailand]

01:08:51.640 --> 01:08:52.500
PD: The final prize
is a royal cuisine banquet.

01:08:52.500 --> 01:08:57.540
[The final prize
is a royal cuisine banquet]

01:08:58.300 --> 01:09:00.500
[Which team will win this game?]

01:09:02.680 --> 01:09:05.040
Commander R: The name tag
ripping game starts now.

01:09:05.040 --> 01:09:05.580
We must win.

01:09:05.580 --> 01:09:06.560
[We must win, we must win]

01:09:06.560 --> 01:09:07.420
Commander R: 5.

01:09:08.120 --> 01:09:08.220
Blue Demon Team.

01:09:08.220 --> 01:09:08.600
[Blue Demon]

01:09:08.600 --> 01:09:09.460
Commander R: 4.

01:09:10.560 --> 01:09:10.620
Commander R: 3.

01:09:10.620 --> 01:09:11.200
[Pink is here to save the world, yay]

01:09:11.200 --> 01:09:12.080
Savior Team.

01:09:12.920 --> 01:09:13.240
Commander R: 2.

01:09:13.240 --> 01:09:13.560
[Yellow Team: Cleaver]

01:09:13.560 --> 01:09:14.290
Yellow Team.

01:09:14.660 --> 01:09:16.000
Cleaver.

01:09:16.000 --> 01:09:16.859
Commander R: 1.

01:09:17.279 --> 01:09:18.939
Commander R: The game begins.

01:09:20.420 --> 01:09:24.700
[Yellow Team's first player
Daou enters the game]

01:09:27.960 --> 01:09:28.060
Daou: It's so scary.

01:09:28.060 --> 01:09:29.279
[Even though it's the third time,
it's still scary]

01:09:29.279 --> 01:09:33.439
Daou: My heart is racing right now
because I don't know who they'll send out.

01:09:33.439 --> 01:09:33.819
Daou: The puzzle thing

01:09:33.819 --> 01:09:36.000
[The more HP you have, the better]

01:09:36.000 --> 01:09:38.060
Daou: really helps us a lot. Trust me.

01:09:38.899 --> 01:09:42.080
[While searching for the Life Card,
a thought comes to mind…]

01:09:42.080 --> 01:09:42.620
Daou: But who knows Maybe they're
secretly planning to team up.

01:09:42.620 --> 01:09:46.220
[But who knows? Maybe they're
secretly planning to team up]

01:09:46.260 --> 01:09:49.460
[If that happens,
what about the other teams?]

01:09:51.580 --> 01:09:53.740
[For the puzzle pieces,
he's not even worried about his knees]

01:09:55.680 --> 01:09:56.580
Off: Where are the puzzle pieces?

01:09:56.580 --> 01:09:58.820
[Blue Team's first player
Off is also looking for the puzzle pieces]

01:10:02.940 --> 01:10:05.840
[Carefully searching every corner]

01:10:05.840 --> 01:10:07.360
Off: Could it be hidden around here?

01:10:07.360 --> 01:10:09.220
Off: Do you think it might be here?

01:10:10.620 --> 01:10:14.340
[Suddenly stepping back?]

01:10:16.260 --> 01:10:18.760
[Jeff from the Pink Team appears]

01:10:18.760 --> 01:10:19.960
Off: Jeff, honestly.

01:10:20.880 --> 01:10:22.540
Off: Why don't we just team up?

01:10:22.700 --> 01:10:24.520
Jeff: That's true.
We should do it that way.

01:10:24.520 --> 01:10:25.400
Off: Let's not hurt each other first.

01:10:25.400 --> 01:10:27.880
Jeff: But we should
pretend we're tearing name tags.

01:10:27.880 --> 01:10:27.940
Jeff: Okay, we have to act like…

01:10:27.940 --> 01:10:30.860
[Off easily opens up to his ally]

01:10:31.360 --> 01:10:31.380
Jeff: Let's find the puzzle pieces first.

01:10:31.380 --> 01:10:32.280
[Anyway, let's go look for
the Life Card puzzle pieces first]

01:10:32.280 --> 01:10:33.080
Off: OK. OK.

01:10:33.940 --> 01:10:37.460
[Trusting Jeff,
then going out to find fragments]

01:10:43.200 --> 01:10:43.340
Phuak: Hello.

01:10:43.340 --> 01:10:44.820
[He sees someone and waves]

01:10:44.820 --> 01:10:45.040
[Jeff runs into the Blue Team]

01:10:45.040 --> 01:10:45.900
Pop: My friend.

01:10:46.040 --> 01:10:48.970
Phuak: Not yet, it's not time
to send new members yet.

01:10:49.300 --> 01:10:50.980
[Quiet]

01:10:51.700 --> 01:10:51.760
[They're about to team up]

01:10:51.760 --> 01:10:54.160
Jeff: Because they have
4 lives over there.

01:10:54.700 --> 01:10:57.140
[Signal to allies: OK]

01:10:57.240 --> 01:10:57.660
Jeff: But we have to act like we're…

01:10:57.660 --> 01:10:58.520
[They decide to become allies]

01:10:58.520 --> 01:10:59.240
Jeff: Fighting each other.

01:10:59.240 --> 01:10:59.700
Jeff: The moment we meet,
we have to show that kind of…

01:10:59.700 --> 01:11:01.060
[If we run into each other…]

01:11:01.340 --> 01:11:02.660
[Pretend we're fighting]

01:11:04.740 --> 01:11:07.940
[Jeff shows a mysterious smile
then turns and walks away]

01:11:08.660 --> 01:11:09.940
[Pretend to fight like this]

01:11:09.940 --> 01:11:10.470
[Now it's okay, right?]

01:11:10.470 --> 01:11:12.420
[Yes.]

01:11:16.160 --> 01:11:16.180
Phuak: This way we'll
have a chance to survive.

01:11:16.180 --> 01:11:17.420
[Yes, we'll win]

01:11:18.340 --> 01:11:18.840
[At our level,
negotiation is nothing]

01:11:18.840 --> 01:11:20.520
Pop: At our level,
it's all about negotiation.

01:11:20.520 --> 01:11:21.600
Phuak: Exactly.

01:11:21.600 --> 01:11:22.020
Pop: One glance
and we understand each other.

01:11:22.020 --> 01:11:23.340
[One look and we know
what the other is thinking]

01:11:25.940 --> 01:11:28.340
[Daou is searching for
puzzle pieces alone]

01:11:31.400 --> 01:11:34.120
[Found someone]

01:11:34.720 --> 01:11:38.560
[He runs into Off who just walked over]

01:11:38.860 --> 01:11:39.480
Daou: Hello, Off Jumpol.

01:11:39.480 --> 01:11:41.120
[Hello, Off]

01:11:41.580 --> 01:11:42.980
Daou: Hello, Off Jumpol.

01:11:44.370 --> 01:11:44.510
Daou: Hello, Off Jumpol.

01:11:44.510 --> 01:11:46.270
[When he realizes Daou is the first
from the Yellow Team, he's very surprised]

01:11:47.070 --> 01:11:47.130
[What are you doing, Off? Wait a second]

01:11:47.130 --> 01:11:49.190
Daou: What are you doing, Off Jumpol?

01:11:50.250 --> 01:11:50.770
Daou: Do you know?

01:11:50.770 --> 01:11:51.890
Off: Looking for the puzzle.

01:11:51.890 --> 01:11:53.220
Daou: You’re alone now.

01:11:54.050 --> 01:11:54.230
Daou: Get ready.

01:11:54.230 --> 01:11:54.970
[Ready]

01:11:54.970 --> 01:11:55.270
Off: But Daou, you can follow me.

01:11:55.270 --> 01:11:57.170
[Daou, you can follow me.]

01:11:57.170 --> 01:11:57.190
Daou: Of course.

01:11:57.190 --> 01:11:58.950
[Of course.]

01:11:59.790 --> 01:12:01.310
[Slowly herding the prey,
little by little]

01:12:03.390 --> 01:12:05.190
[Closing in]

01:12:10.670 --> 01:12:13.230
[Chasing the fleeing Off]

01:12:27.410 --> 01:12:27.470
Off: Where's Jeff? Jeff! Jeff!

01:12:27.470 --> 01:12:30.850
[Off searching for his ally Jeff]

01:12:30.850 --> 01:12:31.390
Off: Jeff, come out, Jeff.

01:12:31.390 --> 01:12:32.930
[At that moment, Jeff suddenly
appears from behind the door]

01:12:32.930 --> 01:12:33.570
Jeff: What?

01:12:33.570 --> 01:12:34.490
Off: Aha!

01:12:34.490 --> 01:12:35.290
Off: Come on.

01:12:35.730 --> 01:12:36.090
Off: Come on.

01:12:36.090 --> 01:12:36.690
Off: Jeff.

01:12:38.690 --> 01:12:38.870
Daou: I only have 1 life, Jeff.
I'm not playing tricks.

01:12:38.870 --> 01:12:41.010
[I only have 1 life.]

01:12:41.010 --> 01:12:42.470
Daou: They told me to pick.

01:12:43.570 --> 01:12:43.630
Off: But they have 4 lives, Jeff.

01:12:43.630 --> 01:12:45.050
[Yellow Team has 4 lives]

01:12:45.050 --> 01:12:46.550
Daou: I'll help you find puzzle pieces
so you can eliminate him.

01:12:46.550 --> 01:12:46.770
[Daou proposes an alliance with Jeff]

01:12:46.770 --> 01:12:48.590
Daou: If we eliminate him,
we'll have time.

01:12:48.590 --> 01:12:48.610
[I'll give you any fragments I find]

01:12:48.610 --> 01:12:50.530
Daou: Once we find the puzzle pieces,
you can take them.

01:12:50.530 --> 01:12:50.670
Jeff: Calm down.

01:12:50.670 --> 01:12:51.930
[I can tell. Stop pretending]

01:12:51.930 --> 01:12:52.150
Jeff: I haven't decided yet.

01:12:52.150 --> 01:12:53.350
[I haven't made a decision yet]

01:12:53.450 --> 01:12:54.380
Jeff: Calm down.

01:12:54.810 --> 01:12:56.050
Jeff: I haven't decided yet.

01:12:56.050 --> 01:12:56.970
Off: Okay, okay.

01:12:56.970 --> 01:12:57.390
Daou: You're at a disadvantage.

01:12:57.390 --> 01:12:57.730
[You don't have any allies]

01:12:57.730 --> 01:12:59.860
Jeff: Let's not make any decision yet.

01:13:02.190 --> 01:13:04.070
[Off avoids Daou
and instead follows Jeff]

01:13:04.170 --> 01:13:04.430
Off: I'll go look around first.

01:13:04.430 --> 01:13:07.190
[Off searches for fragments
during the standoff]

01:13:07.330 --> 01:13:09.060
Off: I'll go look around first.

01:13:10.790 --> 01:13:12.790
[Jeff]

01:13:12.790 --> 01:13:15.510
[Jeff keeps looking back]

01:13:16.430 --> 01:13:20.230
[Daou is following behind]

01:13:20.230 --> 01:13:24.750
[The 2 exchanged a glance]

01:13:24.950 --> 01:13:28.350
[Jeff and Daou seem
to have something going on]

01:13:28.890 --> 01:13:29.190
Daou: Jeff, Jeff.

01:13:29.190 --> 01:13:32.490
[On the way back to the starting point]

01:13:32.490 --> 01:13:32.710
Daou: You and I should team up
and gang up on someone first.

01:13:32.710 --> 01:13:34.630
[You and I should go out first
then fight together]

01:13:35.410 --> 01:13:35.550
Daou: I don't know who they'll send out.

01:13:35.550 --> 01:13:36.530
[I don't know who
the Blue Team will send out, but…]

01:13:36.530 --> 01:13:36.830
Daou: But if it's Off,
he'll be easy to deal with.

01:13:36.830 --> 01:13:38.010
[If we go together,
it'll be easy to handle]
[But it doesn't look like Pop]

01:13:38.010 --> 01:13:39.250
Daou: Phuak would also be easy
to handle. Not...

01:13:39.250 --> 01:13:39.870
Daou: Not Pop.

01:13:39.870 --> 01:13:39.970
[An agreement reached beforehand]

01:13:39.970 --> 01:13:40.850
Jeff: Then I'll go out first.

01:13:40.850 --> 01:13:41.490
Daou: I'll go with you.

01:13:41.490 --> 01:13:42.150
Jeff: Okay.

01:13:44.230 --> 01:13:45.650
[Off is still completely unaware]

01:13:45.650 --> 01:13:46.780
Off: I'm so nervous.

01:13:49.390 --> 01:13:50.870
[Now's the moment]

01:13:59.290 --> 01:13:59.970
Off: Are we starting to rip now?

01:13:59.970 --> 01:14:00.410
Jeff: Come on.

01:14:00.410 --> 01:14:01.170
Off: Are we really doing this?

01:14:01.170 --> 01:14:02.450
Daou: Of course, bro.

01:14:03.930 --> 01:14:05.460
Daou: We have to be serious.

01:14:05.510 --> 01:14:08.230
[Daou & Jeff attack together]

01:14:09.150 --> 01:14:11.830
[Off desperately protects his last life]

01:14:14.990 --> 01:14:17.270
[In the blink of an eye,
he snatches Jeff's name tag]

01:14:18.030 --> 01:14:21.230
[Jeff falls to the ground,
desperately protecting his name tag]

01:14:21.350 --> 01:14:22.090
[Jeff grabs half of the name tag]

01:14:22.090 --> 01:14:23.890
Daou: Got it! Got it!

01:14:23.890 --> 01:14:24.770
Daou: Done.

01:14:24.770 --> 01:14:25.430
Jeff: Daou, rip it!

01:14:25.430 --> 01:14:25.650
[Pass it to Daou to finish the match]

01:14:25.650 --> 01:14:26.710
Jeff: Daou, rip it!

01:14:34.190 --> 01:14:38.430
[According to Daou and Jeff's plan,
Off is eliminated]

01:14:41.830 --> 01:14:41.970
[Even though he fought desperately]

01:14:41.970 --> 01:14:43.770
Daou: I'm really, really sorry.

01:14:43.850 --> 01:14:44.710
Off: It's okay.

01:14:45.370 --> 01:14:46.390
Commander R: Off, eliminated.

01:14:46.390 --> 01:14:49.610
[Off eliminated]

01:14:49.610 --> 01:14:51.130
Commander R: Off, eliminated.

01:14:51.130 --> 01:14:51.730
Off: Okay.

01:14:54.330 --> 01:14:56.490
Commander R: Off, eliminated.

01:14:56.830 --> 01:14:58.130
Darn it.
[Roar…]

01:14:58.130 --> 01:15:00.130
Commander R: Off, eliminated.

01:15:00.770 --> 01:15:01.630
Phuak: Jumpol…

01:15:02.190 --> 01:15:02.730
[Speechless]

01:15:02.730 --> 01:15:03.450
Darn it.

01:15:03.450 --> 01:15:04.330
Pop: What did he say?

01:15:04.330 --> 01:15:04.930
Pop: Didn't he say he'd go out first?

01:15:04.930 --> 01:15:08.210
Phuak: The plan was for the first person
to move flexibly and dodge quickly.

01:15:08.210 --> 01:15:09.010
Pop: What did he go out to look for?

01:15:09.010 --> 01:15:10.850
Phuak: To look for those puzzle pieces.

01:15:10.850 --> 01:15:13.010
Pop: Huh… and the result?
He was the first one eliminated.
[What was that guy even doing?]

01:15:13.010 --> 01:15:14.140
Phuak: Off. Darn it.

01:15:16.370 --> 01:15:19.850
Phuak: Off, what happened?
[Still unaware of Jeff's betrayal]

01:15:19.850 --> 01:15:21.330
Off: When promises
no longer mean anything.

01:15:21.330 --> 01:15:23.130
Off: We had already agreed on it.

01:15:23.130 --> 01:15:24.930
Off: But he didn't keep his word.

01:15:24.930 --> 01:15:27.690
Off: So we must take Jeff out.

01:15:28.000 --> 01:15:32.480
Off: Darn it.
[We must get rid of Jeff]

01:15:33.550 --> 01:15:38.140
[Yellow Team, Pink Team, Blue Team]

01:15:38.390 --> 01:15:40.490
[That took some nerve.
Jeff ran straight to the Blue Team]

01:15:40.490 --> 01:15:42.550
Phuak: Jeff, what happened exactly?

01:15:42.890 --> 01:15:43.230
Jeff: Daou ripped it so suddenly.

01:15:43.230 --> 01:15:44.730
[Naively telling a lie.]

01:15:44.730 --> 01:15:46.390
Jeff: I was running at the time.

01:15:46.390 --> 01:15:49.110
[Check on Daou first]

01:15:51.130 --> 01:15:51.630
Pop: Or was it Jeff who did it?

01:15:51.630 --> 01:15:52.170
[Aren't you the bad guy?]

01:15:52.170 --> 01:15:53.250
Jeff: No, I didn't rip it.

01:15:53.250 --> 01:15:54.570
Phuak: Was it Daou who ripped it?

01:15:54.570 --> 01:15:58.700
Jeff: Daou was hiding in the corner
then suddenly rushed out and ripped it.

01:15:58.970 --> 01:15:59.270
Pop: Can we still trust him?

01:15:59.270 --> 01:16:00.750
[Can Jeff still be trusted?]

01:16:00.770 --> 01:16:02.070
Pop: Can we still trust him?

01:16:02.070 --> 01:16:04.250
[Will Phuak believe Jeff?]

01:16:04.250 --> 01:16:04.550
Phuak: OK.

01:16:04.550 --> 01:16:04.850
[Phuak is being cleverly deceived]

01:16:04.850 --> 01:16:05.210
Jeff: He really is impressive.

01:16:05.210 --> 01:16:06.690
Phuak: According to the original plan,
we're still allies, right?

01:16:06.690 --> 01:16:07.250
Jeff: The original plan.

01:16:07.250 --> 01:16:07.350
Jeff: No problem.

01:16:07.350 --> 01:16:07.730
[Phuak is being cleverly deceived]

01:16:07.730 --> 01:16:10.170
Phuak: There's no choice, bro.
I can only trust him for now.

01:16:10.170 --> 01:16:11.390
Commander R: The second agent,
prepare to enter.

01:16:11.390 --> 01:16:14.190
[Announcement: The second
group of agents enter.]

01:16:14.330 --> 01:16:14.550
Phuak: Pop, watch yourself.

01:16:14.550 --> 01:16:16.470
[Blue Team's second agent to enter: Pop]

01:16:16.650 --> 01:16:17.430
-Phuak: Protect yourself.
-Pop: Can I stand over there and watch?

01:16:17.430 --> 01:16:17.730
[That guy is watching me from over there]

01:16:17.730 --> 01:16:19.390
Phuak: You can go with Jeff, right?

01:16:19.390 --> 01:16:20.370
[Phuak still believes Jeff,
but warns him to be careful of Jeff]

01:16:20.370 --> 01:16:21.250
Pop: Am we going with Jeff?

01:16:21.250 --> 01:16:23.450
Phuak: Go with Jeff, but watch our back.

01:16:23.870 --> 01:16:26.430
[Turning his back to show trust]

01:16:26.530 --> 01:16:27.510
Pop: Jeff, we should keep some distance.

01:16:27.510 --> 01:16:27.930
[They only have 2 lives,
so Pop is a little cautious]

01:16:27.930 --> 01:16:30.650
Pop: We shouldn't stand this close.

01:16:31.370 --> 01:16:31.870
Pop: If anything happens,
I'll lie down right away.

01:16:31.870 --> 01:16:33.450
[If anything happens,
I'll lie down right away]

01:16:33.450 --> 01:16:34.410
Pop: Jeff.

01:16:35.550 --> 01:16:37.910
[Startled!]

01:16:40.410 --> 01:16:42.410
Jeff: That's just how I always play.

01:16:42.930 --> 01:16:44.970
Jeff: If I promise someone something,
I keep it.

01:16:44.970 --> 01:16:45.920
[Still lying smoothly]

01:16:45.920 --> 01:16:47.450
Pop: I didn't see it myself.

01:16:49.630 --> 01:16:52.230
[So cautious]

01:16:53.420 --> 01:16:54.050
[Pink Team's second agent: Ten]

01:16:54.050 --> 01:16:54.930
Ink: Bye, Ten.

01:16:54.930 --> 01:16:55.970
Ink: Ten, fighting!

01:16:55.970 --> 01:16:56.970
Ink: Do your best!

01:16:57.170 --> 01:16:57.570
Ten: Okay.

01:16:57.570 --> 01:16:59.880
Ink: Let's go.

01:17:01.070 --> 01:17:04.830
[Ten is searching for puzzle pieces
to gain an extra HP]

01:17:05.350 --> 01:17:07.990
[Bends down]

01:17:08.550 --> 01:17:13.350
[If he bends any lower,
he'll end up flat on the ground]

01:17:14.230 --> 01:17:16.750
[Moves close to the ground
like Spider-Man]

01:17:17.350 --> 01:17:20.190
[Is anyone here?]

01:17:25.070 --> 01:17:28.950
[Luckily it's Jeff, from the same team]

01:17:29.490 --> 01:17:32.210
Jeff: Just now, I already eliminated Off.

01:17:33.370 --> 01:17:35.010
Jeff: I teamed up with Daou
and eliminated Off.

01:17:35.010 --> 01:17:38.810
Jeff: But now we have to pretend
we're still on their side.

01:17:38.810 --> 01:17:40.770
Jeff: Even though we already eliminated
1 of their team members.

01:17:40.770 --> 01:17:42.570
Pop: Hey, there are 2 of them now.

01:17:43.290 --> 01:17:44.530
Pop: They're talking.

01:17:44.530 --> 01:17:46.030
Pop: They can't be trusted.

01:17:46.030 --> 01:17:48.890
[Pop keeps his distance,
playing very cautiously]

01:17:48.890 --> 01:17:49.070
Blue: This is my first time
playing Running Man.

01:17:49.070 --> 01:17:51.670
[Yellow Team's second agent: Blue]

01:17:51.670 --> 01:17:55.630
[Can he show his strength
and fight until victory?]

01:17:58.390 --> 01:17:59.890
[He runs into Daou right after starting]

01:17:59.890 --> 01:18:00.610
Daou: I told you so.

01:18:00.610 --> 01:18:01.210
Blue: What do you mean, bro?

01:18:01.210 --> 01:18:02.530
Daou: We're playing for real.

01:18:02.530 --> 01:18:04.690
-Daou: But...
-Blue: Off got eliminated too quickly.

01:18:04.690 --> 01:18:05.110
Daou: I wouldn't call that quick.

01:18:05.110 --> 01:18:06.130
[Even with the advantage,
it's meant to apply more pressure]

01:18:06.130 --> 01:18:07.370
Daou: Now it's getting tricky.

01:18:07.370 --> 01:18:07.590
Daou: Quickly find
the puzzle pieces first.

01:18:07.590 --> 01:18:10.110
[Searching for fragments of the Life Card
is also important]

01:18:10.330 --> 01:18:10.350
Pop: Right in the middle.

01:18:10.350 --> 01:18:12.310
[I'm in the middle]

01:18:12.550 --> 01:18:12.970
[Pop is standing in a very visible spot]

01:18:12.970 --> 01:18:14.170
Pop: What should I do?

01:18:14.310 --> 01:18:18.750
[Completely confused now]

01:18:20.550 --> 01:18:23.490
[Daou is coming down from above.
Hide!]

01:18:23.490 --> 01:18:23.510
Pop: Hide! Hide quickly!

01:18:23.510 --> 01:18:25.350
[Hide! Hide!]

01:18:26.030 --> 01:18:29.930
[The new Running Man friend
quickly hides with Ten's help]

01:18:29.930 --> 01:18:31.370
Daou: Where's Pop, Ten?

01:18:31.650 --> 01:18:33.310
Ten: Pop? I don't know either.

01:18:38.430 --> 01:18:41.150
[Did Daou not see
Pop hiding?]

01:18:41.510 --> 01:18:43.870
[Did he walk past?]

01:18:46.390 --> 01:18:50.070
[Daou circles back from behind]

01:18:50.250 --> 01:18:51.050
Daou: Hello.

01:18:51.390 --> 01:18:54.870
[What was that sound?]

01:18:55.210 --> 01:18:56.010
Daou: Hello.

01:19:01.830 --> 01:19:02.050
[The ambush stakeout backfires]

01:19:02.050 --> 01:19:04.510
Daou: It's coming off!
It's coming off, Pop!

01:19:07.930 --> 01:19:09.240
Daou: It's coming off!
It's coming off, Pop!

01:19:09.240 --> 01:19:11.000
[He immediately launch a second attack]

01:19:11.000 --> 01:19:11.060
[The second attack also fails]

01:19:11.060 --> 01:19:12.320
Daou: It's coming off!

01:19:12.380 --> 01:19:13.460
Daou: Quick! Hurry!

01:19:13.460 --> 01:19:14.830
Daou: Blue! Blue! Blue!

01:19:14.830 --> 01:19:16.380
[Because of the skill gap,
Pop begins to counterattack]

01:19:16.380 --> 01:19:17.700
Daou: Blue! Blue! Blue!

01:19:17.700 --> 01:19:18.070
Blue: Coming!

01:19:18.070 --> 01:19:18.940
[Blue arrives!]

01:19:18.940 --> 01:19:19.600
Daou: Blue!

01:19:22.230 --> 01:19:23.300
[Pop is grabbed in an instant]

01:19:23.300 --> 01:19:24.260
Daou: Blue, let's go together.

01:19:24.260 --> 01:19:25.300
Daou: Blue, together.

01:19:25.300 --> 01:19:26.140
Daou: Blue, let's go together.

01:19:26.140 --> 01:19:27.270
Daou: Come on, Blue.

01:19:27.780 --> 01:19:28.070
Daou: Oh man, Pop!

01:19:28.070 --> 01:19:31.190
[Pop falls to the ground]

01:19:31.310 --> 01:19:32.790
[At this very moment]

01:19:32.790 --> 01:19:34.350
[Pop's finishing move fails]

01:19:36.380 --> 01:19:37.940
Jeff: Hey, hey!

01:19:37.940 --> 01:19:39.140
Daou: Should we, bro?

01:19:40.260 --> 01:19:41.020
Pop: You can't take me down.

01:19:41.020 --> 01:19:42.260
Daou: If this were Werewolf...

01:19:42.260 --> 01:19:43.500
Pop: Then I'd just do this.

01:19:43.500 --> 01:19:44.660
Pop: Lie here for another hour.

01:19:44.660 --> 01:19:47.060
Jeff: Let's split up
and look for puzzle pieces first.

01:19:47.060 --> 01:19:47.390
Daou: Blue, make your move. Flip him over.

01:19:47.390 --> 01:19:48.820
[Jeff steps in to mediate
while observing from the side]

01:19:48.820 --> 01:19:49.500
Daou: Flip him.

01:19:49.500 --> 01:19:51.430
Daou: Jeff and I won't do anything.

01:19:51.630 --> 01:19:52.620
[But the Yellow Team
doesn't give up just yet]

01:19:52.620 --> 01:19:54.280
Daou: Flip him. That's right.

01:19:55.990 --> 01:19:59.580
[Protecting himself with quick movements]

01:19:59.580 --> 01:20:00.940
Daou: Do you really
want to play like this,
just lying there the whole time?

01:20:00.940 --> 01:20:01.580
Pop: Yes, yes.

01:20:01.580 --> 01:20:02.700
Pop: I'm leaving.

01:20:02.700 --> 01:20:04.300
Pop: That's how I'm playing.

01:20:04.700 --> 01:20:05.820
Jeff: Let him go for now.
Let him go first.

01:20:05.820 --> 01:20:06.260
Daou: Let's go, Blue.

01:20:06.260 --> 01:20:08.260
Jeff: Not now.
We can't flip him right now.

01:20:08.260 --> 01:20:09.120
Daou: Blue, go.

01:20:09.950 --> 01:20:10.100
[Because of Jeff's persuasion
and the strength gap]

01:20:10.100 --> 01:20:11.420
Blue: Let's leave Pop for now.

01:20:11.420 --> 01:20:13.150
Daou: We were so close just now.

01:20:14.510 --> 01:20:17.790
[Pop survived]

01:20:18.150 --> 01:20:19.620
[If he were eliminated, the Blue Team
would be left with only 1 HP]

01:20:19.620 --> 01:20:20.950
Pop: I'd better go hide.

01:20:23.980 --> 01:20:24.270
Commander R: The remaining agents
join the game.

01:20:24.270 --> 01:20:28.150
[Announcement: The final
member is entering the game]

01:20:28.830 --> 01:20:29.860
[The Yellow Team runs toward NuNew]

01:20:29.860 --> 01:20:30.660
Daou: NuNew, come down! NuNew!

01:20:30.660 --> 01:20:31.260
Blue: NuNew!

01:20:31.260 --> 01:20:32.100
Daou: NuNew, come down.

01:20:32.100 --> 01:20:34.560
NuNew: Oh wow, he actually
came to pick me up.

01:20:36.550 --> 01:20:38.420
[Finally coming out]

01:20:38.420 --> 01:20:39.500
Daou: Am I pretty impressive, bro?

01:20:39.500 --> 01:20:40.260
NuNew: Very impressive.

01:20:40.260 --> 01:20:40.860
Daou: Really?

01:20:40.860 --> 01:20:40.990
NuNew: Then how did you
rip Off's name tag?

01:20:40.990 --> 01:20:42.300
[Daou wants NuNew's praise]

01:20:42.300 --> 01:20:43.180
Daou: We just went at him together.

01:20:43.180 --> 01:20:44.840
Blue: Bro, I think Pop is here.

01:20:44.900 --> 01:20:45.540
Daou: Pop?

01:20:45.540 --> 01:20:46.220
Daou: Really?

01:20:46.220 --> 01:20:48.990
Blue: Because we were downstairs
and didn't run into anyone.

01:20:48.990 --> 01:20:49.060
[We're going bear hunting now]

01:20:49.060 --> 01:20:51.860
Daou: We're
going to hunt the bear, NuNew.

01:20:52.220 --> 01:20:52.230
Daou: Not just any bear,
a giant one.

01:20:52.230 --> 01:20:54.140
[Right from the start,
the Yellow Team goes all out]

01:20:54.140 --> 01:20:55.940
Daou: NuNew, make sure you grab him.

01:20:55.940 --> 01:20:56.030
Daou: We'll lock him down.

01:20:56.030 --> 01:20:57.100
[Heading to attack Pop again]

01:20:57.100 --> 01:20:59.220
Daou: Remember,
NuNew goes in last.

01:21:00.230 --> 01:21:03.030
[On the way to attack Pop again]

01:21:03.580 --> 01:21:05.300
Daou: No, this is the chapel.

01:21:07.150 --> 01:21:09.030
[NuNew notices something]

01:21:09.420 --> 01:21:09.470
NuNew: Huh? What's this?

01:21:09.470 --> 01:21:11.270
[Huh? What's this?]

01:21:13.540 --> 01:21:14.100
NuNew: What is this?

01:21:14.100 --> 01:21:15.160
Daou: NuNew, nice!

01:21:16.030 --> 01:21:16.860
[They find a puzzle piece
hidden deep inside a flowerpot]

01:21:16.860 --> 01:21:17.740
Blue: Where did you find it?

01:21:17.740 --> 01:21:18.340
NuNew: Right here.

01:21:18.340 --> 01:21:19.900
Daou: Okay, okay, okay.

01:21:19.900 --> 01:21:20.900
NuNew: Oh my gosh.

01:21:20.910 --> 01:21:24.950
[4 HP + 1 puzzle piece]

01:21:25.700 --> 01:21:27.220
NuNew: Wow, I'm so proud.

01:21:27.500 --> 01:21:27.710
Daou: NuNew is amazing.

01:21:27.710 --> 01:21:28.500
[NuNew shows his skills
as soon as he joins]

01:21:28.500 --> 01:21:29.630
NuNew: I'm so proud.

01:21:29.980 --> 01:21:30.950
Daou: You're awesome!

01:21:30.950 --> 01:21:30.980
[Lucky NuNew]

01:21:30.980 --> 01:21:32.780
NuNew: I just happened to see it.

01:21:33.500 --> 01:21:35.630
Commander R: The remaining
agents join the game.

01:21:35.630 --> 01:21:41.270
[Each team now has 2 HP;
Pink Team: Ink, Blue Team: Phuak; Set off]

01:21:42.380 --> 01:21:42.830
Phuak: No one here.

01:21:42.830 --> 01:21:43.100
[Step one: Go find teammate "Pop"]

01:21:43.100 --> 01:21:44.160
Phuak: No one here.

01:21:44.220 --> 01:21:45.280
Phuak: No one here.

01:21:47.150 --> 01:21:49.460
[Carefully walking in alone]

01:21:49.460 --> 01:21:50.260
Phuak: Bro.

01:21:51.380 --> 01:21:51.990
Phuak: Bro.

01:21:51.990 --> 01:21:53.380
[He finds Pop hiding here.
Startled!]

01:21:53.380 --> 01:21:54.310
Phuak: I'm here.

01:21:54.420 --> 01:21:54.630
Pop: Why did you come here?
Go somewhere else.

01:21:54.630 --> 01:21:56.500
[Pop drives his teammate away]

01:21:56.500 --> 01:21:57.230
Phuak: Take care of yourself, bro.
We won't stick together then.

01:21:57.230 --> 01:21:58.660
[Now the Blue Team
has switched to solo mode]

01:21:58.660 --> 01:21:59.460
-Phuak: Let's move separately.
-Pop: Don't stay together.

01:21:59.460 --> 01:22:00.020
Phuak: I'm leaving now.

01:22:00.020 --> 01:22:00.820
Pop: Go ahead.

01:22:00.980 --> 01:22:01.980
Phuak: Take care of yourself, bro.

01:22:01.980 --> 01:22:03.780
Phuak: No matter what happens,
just lie down first.

01:22:03.780 --> 01:22:03.830
Pop: Lie down, of course.

01:22:03.830 --> 01:22:06.270
[Of course!]

01:22:06.270 --> 01:22:06.620
[That scared me to death]

01:22:06.620 --> 01:22:08.350
Phuak: That scared me to death.

01:22:08.580 --> 01:22:08.990
Ink: Hey, Jeff.

01:22:08.990 --> 01:22:10.100
[The Pink Team has now
gathered all 3 agents]

01:22:10.100 --> 01:22:10.780
Ink: Who is it?

01:22:10.780 --> 01:22:12.440
Jeff: It's Phuak. It's Phuak.

01:22:12.940 --> 01:22:13.230
Jeff: I talked with Pop for a while,
but Pop doesn't really trust me.

01:22:13.230 --> 01:22:15.180
[I feel like Pop doesn't trust me]

01:22:15.180 --> 01:22:17.110
Phuak: Yeah, Pop doesn't trust you,
but I trust you.

01:22:17.110 --> 01:22:18.020
[I truly trust you]

01:22:18.020 --> 01:22:19.750
Phuak: I trust you completely.

01:22:20.700 --> 01:22:20.830
Phuak: I trust you completely.

01:22:20.830 --> 01:22:24.390
[Looks like he still doesn't know]

01:22:24.750 --> 01:22:27.990
[As expected of Phuak, still cautious
and not lowering his guard]

01:22:28.550 --> 01:22:32.030
[Jeff suggests forming an alliance
to attack the Yellow Team together]

01:22:32.470 --> 01:22:36.670
[A counterattack plan:
Let the fast Ten make the move]

01:22:36.940 --> 01:22:37.740
Phuak: Okay.

01:22:37.910 --> 01:22:41.470
[In the end,
will Phuak truly trust Jeff?]

01:22:41.580 --> 01:22:41.750
Daou: To be honest,

01:22:41.750 --> 01:22:43.100
[Extremely confident]

01:22:43.100 --> 01:22:46.140
Daou: I have great faith
in myself, Blue, and you.
No one can defeat us.

01:22:46.140 --> 01:22:49.160
Blue: Honestly, right now,

01:22:49.160 --> 01:22:49.590
I feel like the Pink Team
and Blue Team have already made a deal.

01:22:49.590 --> 01:22:52.180
[Blue is worried about being surrounded]

01:22:52.180 --> 01:22:53.660
Daou: I think so too.

01:22:53.660 --> 01:22:55.720
Blue: They'll definitely attack us.

01:22:57.260 --> 01:22:57.980
Ink: Where are you going?

01:22:57.980 --> 01:22:59.380
Jeff: I'll lure him over.

01:22:59.630 --> 01:23:01.940
[Jeff walks upstairs alone
to find the Blue Team]

01:23:01.940 --> 01:23:02.740
Ink: Okay.

01:23:02.750 --> 01:23:04.990
[While Jeff is away,]

01:23:04.990 --> 01:23:08.030
[Ink is searching for puzzle pieces]

01:23:11.430 --> 01:23:13.190
[Got it!]

01:23:16.750 --> 01:23:19.990
[A life-extension puzzle piece?]

01:23:20.950 --> 01:23:24.230
[Let's check the corner first]

01:23:27.310 --> 01:23:30.310
[Ink found the life-extension
puzzle piece!]

01:23:31.230 --> 01:23:32.980
[So thrilled she has
to call Jeff over to witness it]

01:23:32.980 --> 01:23:33.910
Ink: Jeff, Jeff!

01:23:35.270 --> 01:23:37.140
[The Yellow Team comes upstairs]
[Daou: Let's go! Check downstairs]

01:23:37.140 --> 01:23:39.470
Daou: Come on, let's go check downstairs.

01:23:45.670 --> 01:23:50.670
[Ten is lying in wait]

01:23:51.860 --> 01:23:53.190
Daou: Come, come, come!

01:23:55.260 --> 01:23:55.670
Jeff: Ten! Ten! Ten!

01:23:55.670 --> 01:23:57.270
[Calling Ten over to prepare the plan]

01:23:57.590 --> 01:23:59.340
[Ten appears. The prey is ready]

01:23:59.340 --> 01:24:01.200
NuNew: Why are you charging at us?

01:24:02.070 --> 01:24:02.580
[Using the pillar as a refuge]

01:24:02.580 --> 01:24:03.380
Daou: Blue.

01:24:03.540 --> 01:24:04.700
Daou: NuNew, stand with
your back against the wall.

01:24:04.700 --> 01:24:06.300
Daou: Back against the wall.

01:24:06.750 --> 01:24:07.780
[The Blue Team begins closing in]

01:24:07.780 --> 01:24:10.310
Daou: Bro, are you sure
you want to surround us like this?

01:24:10.310 --> 01:24:10.500
[Quickly look for a safe spot]

01:24:10.500 --> 01:24:11.960
Pop: Should we go in, boss?

01:24:13.540 --> 01:24:16.270
Daou: Are you sure?
So this is your choice, right?

01:24:16.380 --> 01:24:17.780
Daou: Alright, Mr. Jeff.

01:24:17.980 --> 01:24:19.260
Daou: Make your choice.

01:24:19.260 --> 01:24:20.860
Daou: You chose to betray me!

01:24:21.580 --> 01:24:22.940
Daou: You chose to betray me!

01:24:22.940 --> 01:24:24.400
Jeff: I didn't betray him.

01:24:24.900 --> 01:24:25.700
Phuak: What's going on?

01:24:25.700 --> 01:24:27.020
Phuak: Okay, it's fine.

01:24:27.020 --> 01:24:28.750
Phuak: That guy is too cunning.

01:24:28.940 --> 01:24:30.860
Phuak: Compared to Daou,

01:24:30.860 --> 01:24:32.260
Phuak: I trust Jeff more.

01:24:32.820 --> 01:24:33.980
Daou: Do you know, bro?

01:24:33.980 --> 01:24:36.670
Daou: Jeff is the one
who eliminated your teammate.

01:24:36.670 --> 01:24:36.780
[All 3 teams gather in the same place]

01:24:36.780 --> 01:24:37.580
Daou: Heh.

01:24:38.100 --> 01:24:39.980
Daou: I didn't trick you. I didn't.

01:24:39.980 --> 01:24:41.620
Daou: If you think
you can beat me, then come on.

01:24:41.620 --> 01:24:42.540
Daou: Blue and I move faster.

01:24:42.540 --> 01:24:43.780
Phuak: I only have 1 path left.

01:24:43.780 --> 01:24:46.660
Phuak: If I don't work with him,
I'll still lose to you, Daou.

01:24:46.660 --> 01:24:49.320
Daou: Even if you cooperate,
you'll still lose.

01:24:50.060 --> 01:24:51.060
Daou: Blue! Blue!

01:24:51.060 --> 01:24:51.790
Daou: NuNew!

01:24:52.340 --> 01:24:52.900
Daou: Don't die!

01:24:52.900 --> 01:24:53.830
Daou: Fall back!

01:24:54.900 --> 01:24:56.300
Daou: Don't let them surround us!

01:24:56.300 --> 01:24:57.060
Blue: Something feels off.

01:24:57.060 --> 01:24:57.620
Daou: No, no, no.

01:24:57.620 --> 01:24:58.180
Daou: Don't be afraid.

01:24:58.180 --> 01:24:59.540
Daou: We have more people.

01:24:59.540 --> 01:25:01.590
Daou: And we also have puzzle pieces.

01:25:01.590 --> 01:25:07.260
[Blue Team & Pink Team join forces]

01:25:07.260 --> 01:25:07.860
Jeff: Go around.

01:25:07.860 --> 01:25:08.180
Jeff: Go that way.

01:25:08.180 --> 01:25:08.460
Jeff: Go that way.

01:25:08.460 --> 01:25:08.820
Jeff: Go that way.

01:25:08.820 --> 01:25:09.820
Jeff: Go that way.

01:25:10.060 --> 01:25:11.300
Phuak: Go, go, go!

01:25:11.300 --> 01:25:12.020
Phuak: Go!

01:25:12.020 --> 01:25:12.820
Phuak: Go!

01:25:18.900 --> 01:25:20.340
Daou: Are you trying to surround us?

01:25:20.340 --> 01:25:21.740
Daou: This is a surround attack, right?
That's the plan.

01:25:21.740 --> 01:25:23.400
Phuak: Drive them over there.

01:25:25.660 --> 01:25:27.460
Jeff: Where are they running to?

01:25:28.740 --> 01:25:29.620
Pop: Oh man.

01:25:30.260 --> 01:25:31.520
Pop: Jeff is ruthless.

01:25:31.620 --> 01:25:33.880
Phuak: He's forcing 3 people by himself.

01:25:34.260 --> 01:25:36.320
Blue: Wow, there's nowhere to go now.

01:25:41.900 --> 01:25:45.340
Daou: Let's lure him over first.

01:25:46.100 --> 01:25:48.100
Pop: Let's go. I'll watch your back.

01:26:27.100 --> 01:26:28.900
Phuak: Got it! Got it!

01:26:28.900 --> 01:26:30.700
Phuak: Got it! Got it!

01:26:33.300 --> 01:26:35.220
Phuak: Daou!

01:26:35.220 --> 01:26:35.310
Commander R: NuNew, eliminated.

01:26:35.310 --> 01:26:38.380
[Daou & NuNew are eliminated]

01:26:38.380 --> 01:26:41.140
Commander R: NuNew, eliminated.

01:26:48.540 --> 01:26:51.000
NuNew: Oh, are you here
to take me away again?

01:26:51.460 --> 01:26:53.820
NuNew: On this day of our defeat,

01:26:53.820 --> 01:26:55.980
NuNew: at least there's
this bodyguard

01:26:55.980 --> 01:26:57.710
NuNew: waiting to take me away.

01:26:58.020 --> 01:27:00.150
NuNew: Can you carry me away this time?

01:27:01.220 --> 01:27:02.430
NuNew: Can you carry me?

01:27:02.430 --> 01:27:02.700
[Kitten NuNew's unfulfilled wish]

01:27:02.700 --> 01:27:05.420
NuNew: I didn't come last episode.
Can you carry me this time?

01:27:05.420 --> 01:27:08.020
NuNew: Please, I'm the second
one eliminated.

01:27:08.860 --> 01:27:11.320
NuNew: I'll try my best
to make him pick me up.

01:27:11.940 --> 01:27:12.740
NuNew: Right?

01:27:15.820 --> 01:27:17.820
NuNew: He's not talking to me again.

01:27:18.100 --> 01:27:19.980
NuNew: We've run into each other
at least 10 times already.

01:27:19.980 --> 01:27:22.380
NuNew: I believe one day he'll soften up

01:27:22.380 --> 01:27:25.340
NuNew: and carry me
to the eliminated zone.

01:27:31.350 --> 01:27:33.830
[Phuak is seriously searching
for puzzle pieces]

01:27:38.300 --> 01:27:39.100
Pop: Phuak!

01:27:40.140 --> 01:27:40.940
Pop: Phuak!

01:27:41.980 --> 01:27:43.640
Phuak: Huh? Is Pop calling me?

01:27:44.150 --> 01:27:45.140
[Pop's scream]

01:27:45.140 --> 01:27:46.100
Phuak: Pop called me.

01:27:46.100 --> 01:27:47.430
Phuak: What should I do?

01:27:52.100 --> 01:27:52.190
Commander R: Pop eliminated.

01:27:52.190 --> 01:27:55.340
[Pop eliminated]

01:27:55.340 --> 01:27:57.060
Commander R: Pop eliminated.

01:27:57.740 --> 01:27:59.470
Phuak: Was his name tag ripped?

01:28:02.580 --> 01:28:05.110
Pop: Does Phuak know?
In a moment, Phuak will…

01:28:06.260 --> 01:28:08.660
Pop: I tried hard to shout
his name just now.

01:28:09.420 --> 01:28:10.950
Pop: Not sure if he heard me.

01:28:16.190 --> 01:28:18.750
[Pop is eliminated]

01:28:18.750 --> 01:28:22.670
[But what happened before that?]

01:28:29.260 --> 01:28:30.390
Jeff: Phuak! Phuak!

01:28:32.500 --> 01:28:33.140
Jeff: Bro!

01:28:33.140 --> 01:28:33.270
Jeff: Pop's name tag was ripped by Blue.

01:28:33.270 --> 01:28:35.340
[Pop's name tag was ripped by Blue!]

01:28:35.340 --> 01:28:36.870
Jeff: Pop's name tag was ripped by Blue.

01:28:36.870 --> 01:28:39.870
[Was it really Blue who ripped it?]

01:28:40.470 --> 01:28:44.190
[What is the truth?]

01:28:44.390 --> 01:28:49.550
[Phuak'll avenge this]

01:28:51.380 --> 01:28:52.900
Phuak: Alright, let's
deal with Blue first.

01:28:52.900 --> 01:28:54.830
Jeff: Surround him,
surround him.

01:28:55.660 --> 01:28:56.660
Phuak: Right now,

01:28:59.580 --> 01:29:01.820
Phuak: they still think I'm on their team.

01:29:01.820 --> 01:29:01.990
Phuak: I'm going to give them prey.

01:29:01.990 --> 01:29:04.260
[Phuak: "I'm going hunting now
because I'm really hungry for it."]

01:29:04.260 --> 01:29:05.920
Phuak: I'm really hungry now.

01:29:10.180 --> 01:29:13.260
Blue: Right now I really want to know

01:29:13.260 --> 01:29:14.390
Blue: which one from the Pink Team
ripped Pop's name tag.

01:29:14.390 --> 01:29:14.500
[Which agent of the Pink Team
ripped Pop's name tag?]

01:29:14.500 --> 01:29:16.300
Blue: Right now I really want to know

01:29:16.300 --> 01:29:17.950
Blue: which one from the Pink Team
ripped Pop's name tag.

01:29:17.950 --> 01:29:22.830
[Between the 2 of them,
who is telling the truth?]

01:29:22.830 --> 01:29:26.670
[Who is actually telling the truth?]

01:29:45.020 --> 01:29:46.780
Phuak: Blue, be a good boy.

01:29:47.940 --> 01:29:49.340
Blue: Phuak,
are you the only 1 left now?

01:29:49.340 --> 01:29:50.140
Phuak: Yes.

01:29:54.700 --> 01:29:55.940
Phuak: It'll just waste your energy.
Blue: Want to be eliminated now, bro?

01:29:55.940 --> 01:29:58.270
Phuak: Want to waste your strength, Blue?

01:29:59.540 --> 01:30:00.980
Phuak: It'll just waste energy.

01:30:00.980 --> 01:30:01.540
Phuak: Just…

01:30:01.540 --> 01:30:02.180
Phuak: Just…

01:30:02.180 --> 01:30:03.260
Phuak: What should we do?
Should we go rip Ink's name tag together?

01:30:03.260 --> 01:30:04.500
Phuak: Let's go after Ink.

01:30:04.500 --> 01:30:05.900
Blue: Let's go together.

01:30:11.750 --> 01:30:16.630
[The little fox sends a signal
indicating Blue is upstairs]

01:30:23.110 --> 01:30:27.350
[Dashing to the 7th floor]

01:30:39.780 --> 01:30:41.220
Phuak: It's too late, Blue.

01:30:41.220 --> 01:30:42.100
Jeff: Phuak, go around.

01:30:42.100 --> 01:30:43.900
Jeff: Phuak, go around that way.

01:30:44.580 --> 01:30:45.340
Blue: Phuak.

01:30:45.340 --> 01:30:45.860
Phuak: See that?

01:30:45.860 --> 01:30:47.100
Blue: You're the only one
left now, right, bro?

01:30:47.100 --> 01:30:47.260
Phuak: Yes.

01:30:47.260 --> 01:30:48.420
Blue: So that means the 2 of us...

01:30:48.420 --> 01:30:48.940
Phuak: It's nothing.

01:30:48.940 --> 01:30:50.140
Phuak: It's nothing.

01:31:00.230 --> 01:31:06.350
[Blue is completely surrounded]

01:31:11.340 --> 01:31:11.980
Jeff: Ten.

01:31:11.980 --> 01:31:12.780
Jeff: Rip it!

01:31:14.220 --> 01:31:16.910
[Phuak's hand!]

01:31:27.620 --> 01:31:29.020
Phuak: Wait, wait, wait!

01:31:30.860 --> 01:31:34.660
[Although Phuak ripped Blue's name tag,
but...]

01:31:38.380 --> 01:31:39.980
Phuak: Wait, wait!

01:31:40.500 --> 01:31:42.100
Phuak: Wait, wait!

01:31:43.940 --> 01:31:44.220
Phuak: Wait, hold on!

01:31:44.220 --> 01:31:47.120
[Little fox Ten quickly
rips Phuak's name tag too!]

01:31:47.420 --> 01:31:47.860
Commander R: Phuak, eliminated.

01:31:47.860 --> 01:31:50.780
[Phuak, eliminated]
[Blue, eliminated]

01:31:50.780 --> 01:31:52.780
Commander R: Blue, eliminated.

01:31:56.780 --> 01:31:58.160
[Blue Team: All Members Eliminated]

01:31:58.160 --> 01:31:59.550
[Yellow Team: 1 HP | Pink Team: 2 HP |
Blue Team: 0 HP]

01:31:59.620 --> 01:32:00.880
Jeff: I'm sorry, guys.

01:32:01.900 --> 01:32:04.700
Jeff: I played you all completely.
I told you to fight each other.

01:32:04.700 --> 01:32:06.360
I told you to fight each other.

01:32:07.700 --> 01:32:09.310
[Sorry, guys]

01:32:09.900 --> 01:32:12.590
[What do you mean by that?]

01:32:12.700 --> 01:32:18.070
[Actually, the Pink Team's plan was…]

01:32:18.180 --> 01:32:19.300
Ink: Can we hide in this room?
Go inside and hide.

01:32:19.300 --> 01:32:20.860
[30 minutes earlier]

01:32:20.860 --> 01:32:21.420
Jeff: Yes, yes.

01:32:21.420 --> 01:32:22.060
Ink: Bye-bye.

01:32:22.060 --> 01:32:23.020
Ten: In this room?

01:32:23.020 --> 01:32:23.540
Ten: Okay.

01:32:23.540 --> 01:32:25.100
Ten: Later, lure the prey
into this room.

01:32:25.100 --> 01:32:25.960
Jeff: The prey.

01:32:26.980 --> 01:32:30.440
Jeff: He still doesn't know
I'm the reason Off was eliminated.

01:32:30.780 --> 01:32:31.100
Jeff: If...

01:32:31.100 --> 01:32:31.340
[Pretend to chat and guide him,
then rip the name tag directly]

01:32:31.340 --> 01:32:34.270
Jeff: If it looks negotiable,
just rip it right away.

01:32:34.340 --> 01:32:34.860
Ten: Like that?

01:32:34.860 --> 01:32:35.380
Jeff: Exactly.

01:32:35.380 --> 01:32:37.440
Ten: If there's a chance, just rip it.

01:32:37.620 --> 01:32:38.300
Jeff: Yes.

01:32:38.300 --> 01:32:38.900
Ten: Okay.

01:32:39.020 --> 01:32:41.710
[When Pop was hiding on the 7th floor]

01:32:41.780 --> 01:32:42.580
Jeff: Pop.

01:32:45.100 --> 01:32:46.100
Pop: Is he coming?

01:32:46.620 --> 01:32:47.620
Pop: Is he coming?

01:32:48.060 --> 01:32:52.350
[When Pop was hiding on the 7th floor]

01:32:52.540 --> 01:32:54.200
Jeff: We're still allies now.

01:32:54.300 --> 01:32:55.100
Pop: Really?

01:32:57.820 --> 01:32:58.880
Jeff: Yes, really.

01:33:00.940 --> 01:33:01.740
Jeff: Really.

01:33:02.780 --> 01:33:04.620
Pop: Why is he so confident?

01:33:07.140 --> 01:33:08.600
Pop: I'd better run first.

01:33:09.380 --> 01:33:10.420
Ten: Oh! That scared me.

01:33:10.420 --> 01:33:13.110
[A sweet smile that charms your heart]

01:33:13.420 --> 01:33:14.950
Pop: Two people are coming.

01:33:15.340 --> 01:33:16.740
Jeff: Just ran into them.

01:33:18.500 --> 01:33:20.940
Pop: Dear Jeff,
we even performed at a concert together.

01:33:20.940 --> 01:33:21.300
Jeff: Right.

01:33:21.300 --> 01:33:22.540
Pop: And then we sang.

01:33:22.540 --> 01:33:23.300
Pop: We sang together.

01:33:23.300 --> 01:33:24.940
Jeff: Yeah, we sang together.
I liked that.

01:33:24.940 --> 01:33:25.540
Pop: Yes, yes, yes.

01:33:25.540 --> 01:33:26.020
Jeff: Right?

01:33:26.020 --> 01:33:27.100
Pop: Over there—Phuak is downstairs.

01:33:27.100 --> 01:33:28.180
Jeff: Phuak is downstairs?

01:33:28.180 --> 01:33:29.260
Jeff: Wow, selling out
your friend just like that?

01:33:29.260 --> 01:33:31.940
Pop: Why shall we take
such good care of Phuak?

01:33:32.060 --> 01:33:34.140
Jeff: But I… I didn't...

01:33:36.060 --> 01:33:36.820
Pop: Take him out.

01:33:36.820 --> 01:33:37.750
Pop: Blue. Blue.

01:33:38.740 --> 01:33:39.540
Pop: Blue.

01:33:39.660 --> 01:33:40.990
Pop: Blue went that way.

01:33:41.780 --> 01:33:42.580
Pop: Really.

01:33:43.380 --> 01:33:44.380
Pop: Blue went that way.

01:33:44.380 --> 01:33:45.300
Pop: Jeff, my dear friend.

01:33:45.300 --> 01:33:46.020
Jeff: What is it, my friend?

01:33:46.020 --> 01:33:46.820
Pop: Jeff.

01:33:47.140 --> 01:33:49.000
Jeff: You can't get out here, bro.

01:33:50.860 --> 01:33:51.100
Pop: Phuak!

01:33:51.100 --> 01:33:52.700
[Phuak! Phuak!]

01:33:52.700 --> 01:33:53.500
Pop: Phuak!

01:33:54.380 --> 01:33:56.110
Pop: Phuak, he's attacking me!

01:33:58.380 --> 01:33:59.180
Pop: Phuak!

01:34:01.900 --> 01:34:02.820
Jeff: Ten! Ten!

01:34:03.580 --> 01:34:04.380
Pop: Hey!

01:34:05.060 --> 01:34:05.860
Jeff: Ten!

01:34:06.180 --> 01:34:06.980
Pop: Hey!

01:34:08.540 --> 01:34:11.710
[After dealing with the opponent,
he keeps that sweet smile]

01:34:15.020 --> 01:34:15.820
Pop: Goodbye.

01:34:18.980 --> 01:34:23.830
[Giving Pop a sweet boost]

01:34:23.830 --> 01:34:25.420
[The little fox goes out hunting again]

01:34:25.420 --> 01:34:27.150
Commander R: Pop, eliminated.

01:34:28.100 --> 01:34:28.780
[We have to split up quickly]

01:34:28.780 --> 01:34:30.510
Commander R: Pop, eliminated.

01:34:32.540 --> 01:34:35.070
Pop: He threw away your MOU.
Did you know that?

01:34:35.300 --> 01:34:38.860
Pop: I told you.
I saw it in Jeff's eyes from the start.

01:34:39.420 --> 01:34:40.350
Pop: He's a wolf.

01:34:50.420 --> 01:34:51.910
[Starts giving instructions]

01:34:56.740 --> 01:35:00.140
Ink: But what if it fails,
and Blue tears the name tag instead?

01:35:00.820 --> 01:35:01.100
Ink: But what if it fails,
and Blue tears the name tag instead?

01:35:01.100 --> 01:35:05.100
[Blue?]

01:35:08.780 --> 01:35:13.700
[Does Blue still have HP left?]

01:35:17.500 --> 01:35:20.990
[Blue, who should have
been eliminated, appears again]

01:35:21.420 --> 01:35:23.900
Blue: Now Daou

01:35:25.620 --> 01:35:27.100
Blue: has had his name tag ripped.

01:35:27.100 --> 01:35:28.780
Blue: NuNew's name tag
has also been ripped.

01:35:28.780 --> 01:35:30.860
Blue: Now I'm all alone.

01:35:32.900 --> 01:35:36.340
PD: And the team with the most HP left
is the Yellow Team with 4 HP.

01:35:36.340 --> 01:35:40.220
[The Yellow Team has 4 HP]

01:35:40.220 --> 01:35:42.300
Daou: The one with 2 HP is...

01:35:42.300 --> 01:35:43.380
Blue: Who has 2 HP?

01:35:43.700 --> 01:35:43.820
Daou: Blue.

01:35:43.820 --> 01:35:44.460
[Blue has 2 HP]

01:35:44.460 --> 01:35:45.500
Blue: I have two HP?

01:35:45.500 --> 01:35:45.510
Daou: Because I think in this round,
Blue will be the main
attacker on our team.

01:35:45.510 --> 01:35:51.580
[Because Blue is responsible
for attacking opponents]

01:35:58.140 --> 01:36:03.190
[he needs to use the remaining HP to revive]

01:36:03.540 --> 01:36:04.670
Blue: Ink is coming.

01:36:06.900 --> 01:36:09.160
Blue: If it's just 1 person, that's fine.

01:36:09.940 --> 01:36:11.870
Jeff: Blue, that side is a dead end.

01:36:12.500 --> 01:36:16.140
Jeff: Even if you run, it's useless.
You'll have to face it eventually.

01:36:16.140 --> 01:36:17.800
Blue: Hey, don't gang up on me!

01:36:18.300 --> 01:36:19.700
Blue: Don't gang up on me!

01:36:28.420 --> 01:36:30.750
Blue: Oh no, are you
forcing me over there?

01:36:45.020 --> 01:36:48.350
Jeff: Go toward the mirrors.
Watch the mirrors, be careful.

01:37:20.300 --> 01:37:21.460
Jeff: Sorry, sorry.

01:37:21.460 --> 01:37:22.340
Ink: Does it hurt?

01:37:22.340 --> 01:37:23.940
Jeff: It doesn't hurt, right?

01:37:23.940 --> 01:37:24.820
Ink: Sorry.

01:37:24.900 --> 01:37:26.300
Blue: Wow, Ten is so fast.

01:37:31.340 --> 01:37:32.740
Blue: Wow, I'm being surrounded.

01:37:32.740 --> 01:37:33.380
[Blue, eliminated]

01:37:33.380 --> 01:37:35.220
Commander R: Blue, eliminated.

01:37:36.220 --> 01:37:38.020
Commander R: Blue, eliminated.

01:37:43.260 --> 01:37:49.150
[The Pink Team wins!]

01:37:52.980 --> 01:37:55.180
Royal Feast.

01:37:55.180 --> 01:37:57.380
Phuak: I'm so jealous.

01:37:59.500 --> 01:38:02.980
PD: And that concludes the
name tag ripping battle.

01:38:03.420 --> 01:38:05.220
PD: The winner is the Pink Team.

01:38:05.220 --> 01:38:10.380
[Watch the uncut version of
Running Man Thailand]

01:38:10.380 --> 01:38:13.240
PD: And the Royal Feast is
the prize for the 3 of them.

01:38:15.900 --> 01:38:18.760
Jeff: I guess only royalty
can enjoy food like that.

01:38:22.980 --> 01:38:23.700
Phuak: Right.

01:38:23.700 --> 01:38:25.100
Ink: I really wish you
could all eat it together.

01:38:25.100 --> 01:38:26.700
Phuak: It's fine, you eat it.

01:38:27.140 --> 01:38:29.140
Off: Royal food isn't really for us.

01:38:31.460 --> 01:38:34.540
Running Man Thailand—
Never Stop Running!

01:38:39.060 --> 01:38:42.500
NuNew: Today, I was already scared
before the game even started.

01:38:42.500 --> 01:38:44.900
Oat: As a real man,
I'll just ask directly.
Are you the ghost?

01:38:44.900 --> 01:38:47.020
Phuak: No.
Then who's the one standing here?

01:38:47.020 --> 01:38:47.740
Oat: Who is it?

01:38:47.740 --> 01:38:48.380
Jeff: Which means the other person is…